articles.title: About this site
articles.description: This website consists of a collection of works done for ISSS608 Visual Analytics and Applications.

articles.title: Visual Analytics
articles.description:
Welcome to the website. This is still a work in progress, where data visualisations will be uploaded weekly.

This website contains my journey of creating data visualisation beyond default, using R and Tableau. This is part of the ISSS608 course by SMU MITB program, by Prof Kam Tin Seong from Jan - Apr 2022. I hope you enjoy it!
